article.title: The Best Memory Cards
article.body: Memory cards are a must-have item for any serious techie, and SD cards are quickly becoming the most popular kind you can find. These tiny cards have come to find a home not just in cameras but drones, video game consoles, tablets, phones, and much more. For speeding up your device and giving it room for all the memories you want to save, a memory card is essential, which is why we've compiled this list of some of the best you can find today. Not all memory cards are created equal, so we came up with three central criteria a card had to meet for us to consider it worth your time: it has to be able to store a lot of data, it should be usable on many different devices, and it should be available at an appealing price point. We found many different cards that managed to stack up to our standards, from the Samsung-specific EVO card to the rugged and versatile Micro Center card from Inland. Inland also offers some of the best bang for your buck, so there are deals to be found. Whatever your memory needs, there's a card on this list to match, so read on and get ready to press "record."
